<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vetra Outreach</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 { color: #222; }
        p { color: #555; }
        .contact-form {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        input, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        button {
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        button:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Vetra Outreach</h1>
        <p>We connect brands with highly engaged, premium audiences.</p>
        <p>Our exclusive network includes high-net-worth individuals, decision-makers, and business professionals.</p>
        <p><strong>Why Work With Us?</strong></p>
        <ul style="text-align: left; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <li>✔️ Targeted outreach to premium customers</li>
            <li>✔️ Personalized email campaigns for better engagement</li>
            <li>✔️ Trusted by brands in luxury, finance, and business services</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <form class="contact-form">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>
            <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
            <textarea placeholder="Your Message" rows="4" required></textarea>
            <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
